blog.name: lovingthemisred
blog.title: Giada 💞
blog.description:
HI! I’m Giada! I’m an Italian /almost/ 22-year-old girl who loves Taylor Alison Swift with her entire heart. She’s the best companion I could’ve had asked for during not only my darkest times, but also the happiest ones. She’s always been there for me and I will always be there for her.

I saw her for the first time in Dublin (#repTour) on June 15th with my best friend, a swiftie just like me, she smiled at us twice while we were holding the rainbow flag and it was the best night of my life.

I also love cats (I have a gorgeous cat named Jesse), TV shows, foreign languages (I study English, Spanish and Chinese) and traveling.

Twitter account:

lovingthemisred // xlovingtayisred.
